description:
Chimney and Gombe show Luffy the secret passage that leads to Robin, and Franky puts on a display of raw punching power thanks to a few bottles of cola!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Fukurou no Gosan! Ore no Cola wa Inochi no Mizu!
Fukurou`s Miscalculation! My Cola Is the Water of Life!
Le mauvais calcul de Fukuro ! Mon cola est ma source de vie !
Ошибка Фукуро! Моя кола - живительная вода!
フクロウの誤算! 俺のコーラは命の水
